snippet.title: Narco Police gameplay (PC Game, 1989)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Narco Police, Dos PC game produced by Iron Byte in 1989 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/narco-police/4197/
It is an interesting game, arcade genre. In this game you get the more action, you're a cop and you have to pass different levels.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Thunder Strike - https://youtu.be/joliQddFldE
Resolution 101 - https://youtu.be/3tOYWhkntzw
Strike II - https://youtu.be/X9DNgQDWvy8
